TUMEPONEA CHUPUCHUPU. ASANTE, LYNN.

459
00:39:25,791 --> 00:39:27,458
Je, inafaa kweli? Hiyo ilikuwa nusura tupatikane.

460
00:39:29,083 --> 00:39:30,833
Kweli, ni 3,000 kwa kila mmoja kwa watu 25.

461
00:39:30,916 --> 00:39:31,750
Unaonaje?

462
00:39:31,833 --> 00:39:32,666
Rinrada!

463
00:39:36,791 --> 00:39:38,375
Hukuandika jina lako kwenye karatasi ya rasimu.

464
00:39:42,625 --> 00:39:45,041
Binti Rinrada, Darasa la 11/3,

465
00:39:45,125 --> 00:39:46,791
na Bwana Banjong, Darasa la 11/1,

466
00:39:46,916 --> 00:39:49,416
<span style="style.default_1">tafadhali fika ofisini kwa mwalimu mkuu mara moja.</span>

467
00:39:52,916 --> 00:39:53,833
Naweza kukuhakikishia.

468
00:39:53,916 --> 00:39:56,166
Kama huniamini, mfanye Tong arudie mtihani.

469
00:39:56,250 --> 00:39:57,791
Hapo ndipo utakapojua ukweli.

470
00:40:03,333 --> 00:40:05,208
Nimewaita ninyi wawili hapa

471
00:40:06,041 --> 00:40:08,750
kwa sababu Thanaphon anasema kulikuwa na udanganyifu.

472
00:40:11,875 --> 00:40:14,375
Kuna seti mbili za makaratasi. Haifai kufanya udanganyifu.

473
00:40:31,666 --> 00:40:33,833
Nitawapa nafasi ya kuniambia ukweli.

474
00:40:34,916 --> 00:40:36,250
Banjong, uliiba mtihani au la?

475
00:40:46,166 --> 00:40:47,875
Tutajua hivi punde.

476
00:40:48,666 --> 00:40:50,708
Thanaphon, Rinrada, mnaweza kuondoka.

477
00:40:51,666 --> 00:40:52,875
Banjong, wewe baki hapa.

478
00:41:03,125 --> 00:41:04,333
Lynn, usiondoke bado.

479
00:41:09,291 --> 00:41:11,500
Namba hizi zinafanya nini kwenye karatasi yako ya kazi?

480
00:41:13,041 --> 00:41:15,625
Hizi si zile namba za kwenye seti yako ya mtihani.

481
00:41:30,916 --> 00:41:33,541
Tafadhali usikamatwe.
Tafadhali usikamatwe.

482
00:41:33,666 --> 00:41:35,375
Tafadhali usikamatwe.

483
00:41:39,916 --> 00:41:40,916
Kila kitu kitakuwa sawa.

484
00:41:41,541 --> 00:41:43,750
Huenda ni kuhusu ufadhili wa masomo.

485
00:41:56,333 --> 00:42:00,000
Iko hivi. Tuna ushahidi kwamba
Lynn aliwafanyia marafiki zake mtihani.

486
00:42:04,083 --> 00:42:04,916
Lynn.

487
00:42:06,208 --> 00:42:07,916
Tuambie kwa nini ulifanya hivi.

488
00:42:09,208 --> 00:42:11,250
Usiponiambia, nitakufukuza shule.

489
00:42:14,541 --> 00:42:15,458
Kwa ajili ya pesa.

490
00:42:19,583 --> 00:42:20,416
Ni kwamba, yaani...

491
00:42:20,833 --> 00:42:23,291
Tong alijaribu kunikodi
nimfanyie mtihani.

492
00:42:23,541 --> 00:42:24,500
Kwa baht 3,000.

493
00:42:28,583 --> 00:42:30,833
Nimesikitishwa sana nawe.

494
00:42:32,333 --> 00:42:33,166
Vit.

495
00:42:33,625 --> 00:42:37,791
Nilimkubali binti yako
kwa sababu alikuwa mwanafunzi mzuri.

496
00:42:38,625 --> 00:42:40,750
Lakini kuwa mwanafunzi mzuri haitoshi.

497
00:42:41,875 --> 00:42:43,583
Anapaswa pia kuwa na tabia njema.

498
00:42:44,666 --> 00:42:47,041
Wewe pia ni mwalimu.
Lazima uelewe.

499
00:42:47,125 --> 00:42:49,458
Kumfanyia rafiki yako mtihani
ni udanganyifu.

500
00:42:49,541 --> 00:42:51,291
Ni ukiukaji mkubwa wa sheria za shule.

501
00:42:52,666 --> 00:42:55,625
Kiukweli, ningeweza kukufukuza sasa hivi.

502
00:42:57,625 --> 00:42:59,166
Lakini kwa kuwa hii ni mara ya kwanza,

503
00:43:00,166 --> 00:43:02,333
Ninasitisha tu
ufadhili wako wa masomo.

504
00:43:10,541 --> 00:43:11,500
Ndiyo, mwalimu.

505
00:43:16,291 --> 00:43:19,750
Je, Tong na Lynn hawawezi kurudia tu mtihani?

506
00:43:23,708 --> 00:43:24,791
Kumbuka, Lynn.

507
00:43:25,583 --> 00:43:27,875
Shule ni mahali pa kusoma,

508
00:43:28,875 --> 00:43:30,208
si mahali pa kutengeneza pesa.

509
00:43:32,166 --> 00:43:33,125
Kuna nini cha kuchekesha?

510
00:43:34,208 --> 00:43:35,541
-Huna adabu.
-Hapana.

511
00:43:35,875 --> 00:43:36,708
Sio hivyo.

512
00:43:36,916 --> 00:43:37,750
Bwana Pravit.

513
00:43:37,958 --> 00:43:40,333
Wewe ni mwalimu. Je, hukumpa mafunzo ya adabu?

514
00:43:44,625 --> 00:43:45,458
Samahani.

515
00:43:47,916 --> 00:43:51,750
Siwezi kuwa peke yangu niliyeitumia shule kama sehemu ya kujipatia pesa.

516
00:43:54,666 --> 00:43:56,000
Unamaanisha nini kusema hivyo?

517
00:43:56,083 --> 00:43:59,125
Nazungumzia 'chai' ambayo baba yangu alilipa.

518
00:44:02,041 --> 00:44:03,791
Haiitwi 'chai'.

519
00:44:04,875 --> 00:44:06,875
Inaitwa ada ya ukarabati wa shule.

520
00:44:07,083 --> 00:44:08,958
Ada ya ukarabati wa shule.

521
00:44:09,666 --> 00:44:10,791
Je, si ni ada ya shule?

522
00:44:10,875 --> 00:44:12,166
Inatosha, Lynn. Inatosha.

523
00:44:20,958 --> 00:44:22,291
Tafadhali mruhusu binti yangu aendelee hapa.

524
00:44:23,250 --> 00:44:24,875
Nitashughulikia ada ya shule iliyobaki.

525
00:44:24,958 --> 00:44:25,833
Twende.

526
00:44:26,958 --> 00:44:27,833
Sawa.

527
00:44:29,083 --> 00:44:30,500
Lakini kuna sharti moja.

528
00:44:33,083 --> 00:44:35,750
Umepigwa marufuku kupata ufadhili wa masomo wa Singapore.

529
00:44:48,791 --> 00:44:49,625
Twende.

530
00:44:49,958 --> 00:44:51,416
Ufadhili wa masomo unahusikaje hapa?

531
00:44:51,833 --> 00:44:53,708
Ni kweli kwamba niliwasaidia rafiki zangu kunakili majibu yangu,

532
00:44:53,916 --> 00:44:55,458
lakini sijawahi kunakili ya mtu mwingine.

533
00:44:56,500 --> 00:44:58,125
Matokeo yote niliyoyapata

534
00:44:58,333 --> 00:45:00,416
yamekuwa matokeo ya uwezo wangu mwenyewe.

535
00:45:00,500 --> 00:45:03,125
Wanafunzi wengine pia wana uwezo kama huo.

536
00:45:03,375 --> 00:45:06,375
Watu kama Thanaphon wanastahili ufadhili huo zaidi.

537
00:45:08,708 --> 00:45:10,416
Kama huwezi kukubali sharti hili,

538
00:45:10,583 --> 00:45:12,125
ni bora uondoke.

539
00:45:13,708 --> 00:45:14,708
Sawa, Vit?

540
00:45:18,000 --> 00:45:18,833
Ndiyo, mwalimu.

541
00:45:19,458 --> 00:45:20,291
Twende.

542
00:45:25,041 --> 00:45:26,750
Kila la heri na ufadhili wa masomo.

543
00:45:42,125 --> 00:45:43,750
Ikiwa ushahidi umepatikana...

544
00:45:45,916 --> 00:45:47,625
basi nahisi huenda Lynn aliiba mtihani.

545
00:45:48,875 --> 00:45:51,500
PONGEZI KWA WANAFUNZI WA UFADHILI
MWAKA WA MASOMO 2013

546
00:45:51,583 --> 00:45:52,833
Lakini mimi sijahusika.

547
00:45:52,916 --> 00:45:54,833
BIBI RINRADA NILTHEP, GREDI YA KUMI NA MOJA

548
00:45:54,916 --> 00:45:57,208
<span style="style.default_1">Sisi sote kuwa wanafunzi bora
haimaanishi kwamba...</span>

549
00:45:57,291 --> 00:45:58,625
BWN. THANAPHON VIRIYAKUL

550
00:45:58,708 --> 00:46:00,208
tuna tabia zinazofanana.

551
00:46:02,833 --> 00:46:04,208
BIBI RINRADA NILTHEP

552
00:46:07,083 --> 00:46:08,000
Kama nilivyofikiria.

553
00:46:08,416 --> 00:46:10,625
Kwa hakika usingefanya hivyo
kwa ajili ya bati 3,000 tu.

554
00:46:13,958 --> 00:46:15,041
Mafunzo ya piano.

555
00:46:19,833 --> 00:46:22,666
Hukuwahi kufikiria
kwamba ingekuwa bora zaidi

556
00:46:22,750 --> 00:46:25,083
kuwafundisha rafiki zako kikweli?

557
00:46:27,291 --> 00:46:28,791
Lakini mwalimu mkuu
alituibia kwanza, Baba.

558
00:46:29,333 --> 00:46:32,791
Unawezaje kuuita wizi
wakati nililipa kwa hiari?

559
00:46:32,875 --> 00:46:33,833
Ndivyo walivyofanya rafiki zangu pia.

560
00:46:33,916 --> 00:46:35,875
Bado huoni
kwamba ulifanya kosa?

561
00:46:52,500 --> 00:46:53,458
Nitabeba lawama.

562
00:46:56,416 --> 00:46:57,250
Ni kosa langu

563
00:46:58,791 --> 00:46:59,958
Siwezi kumlaumu mtu mwingine yeyote.

564
00:47:04,000 --> 00:47:05,583
Ikiwa hata siwezi kukulea
uwe mtu mwema,

565
00:47:06,083 --> 00:47:09,541
nitawezaje kuthubutu kuwaomba watu wengine
walipie ada yako?

566
00:47:18,250 --> 00:47:21,666
Nitauza gari langu kulipia salio
la ada ya shule.

567
00:47:24,708 --> 00:47:25,625
Kuhusu shati hili...

568
00:47:28,916 --> 00:47:29,916
Silihitaji tena.

569
00:47:33,375 --> 00:47:35,208
Na tusahau kuhusu kwenda nje ya nchi.

570
00:47:36,791 --> 00:47:38,000
Huendi popote tena.

571
00:47:38,666 --> 00:47:39,625
Baki hapa na baba yako.

572
00:47:41,333 --> 00:47:43,625
Rudisha pesa zote kwa marafiki zako.

573
00:48:05,583 --> 00:48:08,208
Hata mkifikiria kiasi gani\nkwamba Lynn ni mtu mbaya...

574
00:48:09,708 --> 00:48:13,416
yeye ni rafiki yangu wa dhati.

575
00:48:21,666 --> 00:48:24,000
Samahani kwa kuwa mlalamishi...

576
00:48:25,125 --> 00:48:27,041
lakini sifanyi maigizo tu.

577
00:48:32,375 --> 00:48:36,125
DARASA LA 12

578
00:48:45,416 --> 00:48:47,333
Haya, nimependeza au la?

579
00:48:48,750 --> 00:48:49,625
Siyo mbaya.

580
00:48:50,583 --> 00:48:52,166
Majaribio ya uigizaji ni kesho.

581
00:48:52,500 --> 00:48:54,500
Hujaniita hapa kwa ajili ya hili tu, sivyo?

582
00:48:59,125 --> 00:49:00,541
Mmekuwaje?

583
00:49:00,916 --> 00:49:03,833
Mnaweza kujiangalia wenyewe\nkwa mihula miwili tuliyobaki nayo?

584
00:49:06,666 --> 00:49:10,166
Mimi na Pat tuna mambo mengine\nya kuhangaikia.

585
00:49:15,250 --> 00:49:16,583
Je, Pat amekuambia?

586
00:49:16,833 --> 00:49:18,708
Tumetoka tu kurejea kutoka Ufaransa.

587
00:49:19,375 --> 00:49:21,416
Safari ilikuwa ya kufurahisha sana.

588
00:49:21,500 --> 00:49:23,541
Ndiyo, kwa sababu uliniacha.se. 
-Mama.

589
00:49:23,666 --> 00:49:26,333
Pia nilikununulia kitu-- 

590
00:49:26,416 --> 00:49:28,750
-Pat.\n-Naam?

591
00:49:28,833 --> 00:49:29,916
Niletee divai nyekundu kutoka ghalani.

592
00:49:30,500 --> 00:49:32,083
Kwa nini usimwambie mfanyakazi wa ndani ailete?

593
00:49:32,291 --> 00:49:34,750
Ndiyo, bwana.

594
00:49:42,666 --> 00:49:43,500
Grace, ungependa kitinda mlo zaidi?

595
00:49:51,375 --> 00:49:53,625
Niko sawa, asante.

596
00:49:53,708 --> 00:49:54,625
Tulikualika hapa leo

597
00:49:55,375 --> 00:49:58,541
kwa sababu tulitaka kukushukuru.

598
00:49:58,666 --> 00:50:00,833
Kunishukuru kwa nini?

599
00:50:01,708 --> 00:50:02,916
Kwa kumsaidia Pat katika masomo yake.

600
00:50:03,250 --> 00:50:05,875
For helping Pat with his studies.

601
00:50:06,500 --> 00:50:08,541
Hujui kabisa

602
00:50:09,000 --> 00:50:11,375
jinsi tulivyokuwa na wasiwasi
kuhusu alama zake.

603
00:50:12,000 --> 00:50:14,541
Lakini mara tu ninyi wawili mlipoanza kuwa wapenzi,

604
00:50:15,041 --> 00:50:17,666
Pat amekuwa mtu mpya kabisa.

605
00:50:19,250 --> 00:50:20,416
Nachosema ni kwamba

606
00:50:20,875 --> 00:50:24,750
wewe ni mwerevu kuliko wale
walimu maarufu wote.

607
00:50:30,625 --> 00:50:33,708
Kiukweli, tumekuwa tukipanga
kwa muda sasa

608
00:50:33,875 --> 00:50:37,208
kumpeleka Pat katika chuo kile kile
nilichosoma kule Boston.

609
00:50:38,500 --> 00:50:40,500
Kulingana na alama zake za awali,

610
00:50:41,125 --> 00:50:44,666
najua kwamba hakika hatafaulu.

611
00:50:45,500 --> 00:50:47,416
Hivyo, hiki ndicho ninachofikiria.

612
00:50:49,208 --> 00:50:50,416
Unapaswa kwenda naye,

613
00:50:50,875 --> 00:50:52,375
ili uweze kumsaidia
katika masomo yake huko.

614
00:50:54,125 --> 00:50:55,041
Inasikika vizuri?

615
00:51:07,291 --> 00:51:09,333
Hakuna haja ya kuwa na wasiwasi kuhusu gharama.

616
00:51:09,916 --> 00:51:11,291
Malazi, chakula...

617
00:51:11,500 --> 00:51:12,583
Tutashughulikia kila kitu.

618
00:51:13,208 --> 00:51:15,000
Kuhusu ada ya masomo...

619
00:51:16,708 --> 00:51:18,208
Kama umepungukiwa...

620
00:51:20,625 --> 00:51:21,958
unaweza kuniomba wakati wowote bila wasiwasi.

621
00:51:25,000 --> 00:51:26,541
Tayari nina
taarifa zote hapa.

622
00:51:26,958 --> 00:51:28,458
Tafadhali ziangalie.

623
00:51:33,500 --> 00:51:36,625
Ikiwa pesa si tatizo, sema ndiyo, sawa?

624
00:51:46,833 --> 00:51:48,916
Unajua kuhusu mtihani wa STIC, sivyo?

625
00:51:50,541 --> 00:51:53,208
Ni kama GAT/PAT
kwa kujiunga na vyuo vikuu vya Marekani.

626
00:51:53,291 --> 00:51:55,166
Hufanyika kwa wakati mmoja
duniani kote.

627
00:51:55,375 --> 00:51:56,958
Nahitaji kufanya mtihani wa STIC

628
00:51:57,750 --> 00:52:00,041
na nahitaji kuufanya ndani ya mwaka huu.

629
00:52:01,958 --> 00:52:02,791
Kama nisipofanya,

630
00:52:03,208 --> 00:52:06,416
sitoweza kutuma maombi
kwenye vyuo vikuu kwa wakati.

631
00:52:09,416 --> 00:52:11,208
JINSI YA KUSHINDA STIC

632
00:52:13,416 --> 00:52:15,416
Tayari nimejihatarisha sana kwa ajili yako, Grace.

633
00:52:21,583 --> 00:52:24,166
Ni vigumu sana kwangu kukuomba msaada.

634
00:52:25,541 --> 00:52:27,541
Lakini mimi na Pat kwa kweli hatujui nini kingine cha kufanya.

635
00:52:30,583 --> 00:52:32,916
Pat anasema atakuajiri kwa baht 600,000.

636
00:53:11,583 --> 00:53:15,000
JINSI YA KUSHINDA STIC

637
00:53:18,375 --> 00:53:20,791
Samahani. Unaweza kumrudishia Pat hii?

638
00:53:20,875 --> 00:53:22,000
Sawa.

639
00:53:22,833 --> 00:53:24,750
Naweza kuazima kalamu na karatasi?

640
00:53:26,000 --> 00:53:32,958
KWA KWELI SIWEZI KUKUSAIDIA SAFARI HII, SAMAHANI!

641
00:53:36,333 --> 00:53:37,250
Dada.

642
00:53:38,041 --> 00:53:39,750
Ungependa kuhifadhi chumba?

643
00:55:08,666 --> 00:55:09,791
Kuhusu kanda za muda,

644
00:55:10,541 --> 00:55:13,041
STIC hufanyika kwa wakati na tarehe sawa duniani kote.

645
00:55:14,041 --> 00:55:15,541
Hii inamaanisha nchi hizi hapa

646
00:55:15,708 --> 00:55:17,541
zitafanya mtihani mapema kuliko maeneo mengine.

647
00:55:20,125 --> 00:55:21,250
Kwa ufupi,

648
00:55:21,458 --> 00:55:23,250
ikiwa ninyi wawili mtafanya mtihani nchini Thailand,

649
00:55:23,333 --> 00:55:26,083
wakati mimi nikiufanya mahali ambapo hufanyika mapema,

650
00:55:26,458 --> 00:55:28,041
kama vile Sydney, Australia,

651
00:55:28,541 --> 00:55:30,166
hiyo inamaanisha saa nne mapema kuliko Thailand,

652
00:55:30,666 --> 00:55:32,250
tutaweza kuona maswali ya mtihani mapema zaidi

653
00:55:32,791 --> 00:55:34,125
na kuyajibu mapema pia.

654
00:55:35,041 --> 00:55:37,333
Naweza kuwatumia ninyi majibu

655
00:55:37,708 --> 00:55:39,500
na kwa watu wengine nchini Thailand pia.

656
00:55:39,833 --> 00:55:41,458
Wengi kadiri tunavyotaka.

657
00:55:45,208 --> 00:55:46,208
Kwa kutumia mbinu hii,

658
00:55:46,458 --> 00:55:47,625
si tu nitakuwa nikiwasaidia

659
00:55:47,708 --> 00:55:50,333
kupata alama za kufaulu kuingia chuo kikuu,

660
00:55:51,166 --> 00:55:53,291
nitakuwa nikipata mapato kutoka kwa wateja wengine pia.

661
00:55:54,416 --> 00:55:57,541
Baada ya kukata gharama, tunaweza kugawana faida.

662
00:55:59,958 --> 00:56:01,000
Je, si hatari sana?

663
00:56:02,500 --> 00:56:04,250
Hatari? Hata kidogo.

664
00:56:04,666 --> 00:56:05,541
Huyu ni nani?

665
00:56:05,708 --> 00:56:07,208
Ni Mwalimu Lynn, mpenzi.

666
00:56:07,875 --> 00:56:09,208
Hii ndiyo njia pekee

667
00:56:10,000 --> 00:56:12,083
kwangu mimi kuwa na pesa za kutosha kwenda kusoma na wewe

668
00:56:12,166 --> 00:56:13,708
bila kulazimika kumuomba mtu yeyote msaada.

669
00:56:16,541 --> 00:56:18,458
Oh, nilisahau kutaja.

670
00:56:20,291 --> 00:56:21,916
Nitakwenda Boston na nyinyi nyote wawili pia.

671
00:56:25,250 --> 00:56:27,666
Itakuwa vizuri sana kwenda pamoja!

672
00:56:30,833 --> 00:56:34,708
Nyinyi wawili mtahusika na kutafuta wateja kwa ajili yangu.

673
00:56:35,125 --> 00:56:36,500
Kuhusu mtihani wenyewe,

674
00:56:36,916 --> 00:56:37,750
Nitashughulikia hilo.

675
00:56:38,000 --> 00:56:38,833
Subiri kidogo.

676
00:56:39,583 --> 00:56:41,875
Kabla hatujafika kwenye sehemu ya wateja,

677
00:56:42,333 --> 00:56:44,291
Naelewa kuhusu suala la kanda za saa,

678
00:56:45,041 --> 00:56:46,458
lakini bado nimechanganyikiwa.

679
00:56:46,583 --> 00:56:48,750
Utayatoaje majibu nje ya chumba cha mtihani?

680
00:56:49,750 --> 00:56:50,625
Kuyaandika kwa siri?

681
00:56:51,791 --> 00:56:52,750
Kuyakariri.

682
00:56:55,916 --> 00:56:57,541
Kuyakariri ndiyo njia bora zaidi.

683
00:56:58,041 --> 00:56:59,250
Ndio salama zaidi.

684
00:56:59,666 --> 00:57:00,750
Na haiachi alama yoyote.

685
00:57:01,416 --> 00:57:02,666
Samahani.

686
00:57:03,041 --> 00:57:04,416
Je, wewe ni mmoja wa X-Men?

687
00:57:04,500 --> 00:57:06,875
STIC ina zaidi ya maswali 100.

688
00:57:07,166 --> 00:57:08,875
Je, unaweza kuyakumbuka yote?

689
00:57:09,000 --> 00:57:09,916
Ndiyo, naweza.

690
00:57:10,958 --> 00:57:12,083
Ikiwa nitakuwa na muda wa kutosha.

691
00:57:13,791 --> 00:57:15,750
Lakini, baada ya mimi kumaliza maswali,

692
00:57:15,833 --> 00:57:17,291
hakuna muda mwingi uliobaki.

693
00:57:17,583 --> 00:57:20,500
Ninachoweza kufanya ni kukumbuka nusu tu ya maswali.

694
00:57:20,875 --> 00:57:21,708
Nusu tu?

695
00:57:24,458 --> 00:57:26,083
Kuna mtu mmoja anayeweza kusaidia.

696
00:57:27,083 --> 00:57:28,291
Lakini hataki.

697
00:57:37,416 --> 00:57:38,250
Inakuwaje, Mama?

698
00:57:39,125 --> 00:57:39,958
Ndiyo, nimemaliza.

699
00:57:44,291 --> 00:57:45,541
Nyumbani kwa Bwana Rut?

700
00:57:48,208 --> 00:57:50,041
Je, haiwezi kusubiri mpaka siku nyingine? Kesho?

701
00:57:51,125 --> 00:57:53,125
Nina mtihani wangu wa ufadhili saa mbili asubuhi.

702
00:57:56,000 --> 00:57:56,833
Sawa.

703
00:58:03,916 --> 00:58:04,750
Hey, wewe!

704
00:58:04,833 --> 00:58:06,375
Kikapu chako kimekwaruza kioo changu!

705
00:58:07,000 --> 00:58:07,916
Kama ungesema samahani--

706
00:58:24,875 --> 00:58:25,791
Inauma...

707
00:59:03,416 --> 00:59:04,916
Ni 250,000 kwa alama ya kufaulu.

708
00:59:05,583 --> 00:59:07,000
Hizo si pesa nyingi kwako, au siyo?

709
00:59:07,083 --> 00:59:09,125
Ada ya masomo ya STIC ni ghali zaidi.

710
00:59:09,458 --> 00:59:10,625
Hebu tulifikirie hilo.

711
00:59:11,125 --> 00:59:12,875
Tunahitaji kujaribu kupata wateja 30.

712
00:59:13,083 --> 00:59:14,583
Zaidi ya hapo itakuwa hatari sana.

713
00:59:14,666 --> 00:59:16,750
Chini ya hapo pia haitafaa kitu.

714
00:59:18,708 --> 00:59:21,875
Tayari nina karibu watu 30 kwenye kikundi changu cha STIC.

715
00:59:23,333 --> 00:59:24,958
Ukiwaambia marafiki zako huko wajiunge,

716
00:59:25,500 --> 00:59:28,958
Nitapunguza 5,000 kwenye ile ada unayopaswa kunilipa.

717
00:59:29,833 --> 00:59:30,916
Lakini subiri.

718
00:59:32,166 --> 00:59:34,750
Lazima uhakikishe hakuna anayejua hili.

719
00:59:36,375 --> 00:59:37,666
Hasa yule mzembe, Bank.

720
00:59:37,750 --> 00:59:40,250
Hey, huna haja ya kuwa na wasiwasi na huyo mjinga.

721
00:59:41,041 --> 00:59:42,458
Hatamwambia mtu yeyote.

722
00:59:42,541 --> 00:59:43,375
Kwa nini?

723
00:59:43,875 --> 00:59:44,708
Hukusikia?

724
00:59:46,916 --> 00:59:49,750
Yule bwege alipigwa.

725
00:59:50,166 --> 00:59:51,541
Yuko hospitalini.

726
01:00:01,625 --> 01:00:02,625
Sehemu nzuri zaidi ni kwamba

727
01:00:03,000 --> 01:00:04,833
hakuweza kufika kwenye mtihani wa ufadhili.

728
01:00:12,250 --> 01:00:18,541
SEMINA: KUNG'ARA KATIKA ELIMU

729
01:00:20,125 --> 01:00:22,583
Ninaamini kwamba kila mmoja hapa

730
01:00:22,666 --> 01:00:24,125
anataka kufaulu STIC

731
01:00:25,083 --> 01:00:27,708
ili kutimiza ndoto zao.

732
01:00:28,875 --> 01:00:30,708
Huyo ni Steve Pat.

733
01:00:31,000 --> 01:00:35,583
Nina njia kwa kila mmoja\nkupata alama za kuridhisha.

734
01:00:36,583 --> 01:00:38,416
Vitu pekee unavyoweza kuingia navyo chumba cha mtihani

735
01:00:38,958 --> 01:00:41,333
ni penseli ya 2B, kifutio.

736
01:00:42,666 --> 01:00:43,541
Kitambulisho chako cha mtihani...

737
01:00:44,750 --> 01:00:45,625
Na pasipoti yako.

738
01:00:46,750 --> 01:00:49,916
Vifaa vya mawasiliano\nvimepigwa marufuku kabisa.

739
01:00:50,291 --> 01:00:53,250
Hivyo, nitaficha simu yenye majibu

740
01:00:53,458 --> 01:00:57,083
ili itumwe tena Thailand\nndani ya tangi la maji kwenye choo cha mtihani.

741
01:00:57,833 --> 01:01:00,958
Nitatuma majibu hayo\nwakati wa mapumziko.

742
01:01:01,541 --> 01:01:03,833
Mtihani umegawanywa katika vipindi vitatu,

743
01:01:03,916 --> 01:01:05,166
ukiwa na mapumziko mawili.

744
01:01:06,041 --> 01:01:07,291
Subiri. Sekunde moja tu.

745
01:01:08,083 --> 01:01:10,041
Wateja hupataje\nmajibu ndani ya chumba cha mtihani?

746
01:01:10,125 --> 01:01:11,875
Sio kila mtu anaweza kukariri\nmajibu yote kama wewe.

747
01:01:17,458 --> 01:01:18,333
Barcode.

748
01:01:23,250 --> 01:01:25,250
Kila mmoja atapewa penseli ya 2B

749
01:01:25,333 --> 01:01:26,750
yenye barcode juu yake.

750
01:01:27,208 --> 01:01:29,583
Upana tofauti wa mistari\nkatika kila barcode

751
01:01:29,875 --> 01:01:31,125
itawakilisha jibu tofauti.

752
01:01:31,208 --> 01:01:33,500
Kuanzia kushoto kwenda kulia.

753
01:01:34,291 --> 01:01:36,708
Tukianzia na mstari nene zaidi,
ambao unawakilisha A,

754
01:01:36,791 --> 01:01:39,208
kisha B, C, na D.

755
01:01:40,333 --> 01:01:41,666
Inasikika vizuri, sivyo?

756
01:01:41,958 --> 01:01:43,208
Lakini mambo hayoishii hapo.

757
01:01:43,458 --> 01:01:44,833
Kuna penseli nne.

758
01:01:45,125 --> 01:01:48,166
Penseli moja kwa kila sehemu.

759
01:01:50,000 --> 01:01:54,083
Na hizi namba kando ya msimbo pau
ni kwa ajili ya maswali ya kujaza.

760
01:01:54,166 --> 01:01:55,291
MAJIBU YA KUJAZA

761
01:01:55,458 --> 01:01:59,166
Kwa insha, wanatumia
vifaa ambavyo tayari vimechapishwa.

762
01:01:59,916 --> 01:02:02,125
Nitatuma maneno muhimu,
ili muweze kuyatafuta Google. Semina sasa.

763
01:02:02,208 --> 01:02:03,708
Tutaungana

764
01:02:03,791 --> 01:02:05,958
katika jitihada zetu za kielimu

765
01:02:06,041 --> 01:02:07,541
I'm telling you how to do this,

766
01:02:07,791 --> 01:02:09,458
but you'll have to write
the answers yourselves.

767
01:02:10,166 --> 01:02:12,291
To summarize, on the exam day,

768
01:02:12,708 --> 01:02:16,125
everyone has to leave
the meeting point by 7:30 a.m.

769
01:02:16,500 --> 01:02:18,750
in order to reach the exam rooms in time.

770
01:02:19,083 --> 01:02:24,083
We'll provide a motorbike to take
each person to their exam venue.

771
01:02:24,166 --> 01:02:27,958
Finally, everyone has to pay in cash

772
01:02:28,583 --> 01:02:29,875
within the next two weeks.

773
01:02:30,166 --> 01:02:33,333
Otherwise, the deal is off.

774
01:02:36,375 --> 01:02:38,208
One other thing
I need to emphasize is that...

775
01:02:39,250 --> 01:02:43,083
what we are about to do together
must be kept secret.

776
01:02:44,833 --> 01:02:46,208
Does anyone have any issues?

777
01:02:48,958 --> 01:02:49,833
If not,

778
01:02:50,416 --> 01:02:52,416
we'll end the seminar now.

779
01:02:54,541 --> 01:02:56,583
We will unite

780
01:02:57,041 --> 01:02:59,208
in our educational quest

781
01:03:00,041 --> 01:03:02,833
kupata alama zitakazotuwezesha\nkujiunga na chuo chochote.

782
01:03:03,791 --> 01:03:05,750
Tunahitaji kuweza kuchagua chuo chetu,

783
01:03:05,833 --> 01:03:08,625
sio kukiacha kiamue ikiwa\ntunaweza kusoma hapo au la.

784
01:03:23,791 --> 01:03:25,708
Pole, hiyo ni hali ngumu, Bank.

785
01:03:40,500 --> 01:03:41,416
Kuna nini?

786
01:03:43,291 --> 01:03:44,375
Nilisikitika kusikia kuhusu hilo.

787
01:03:45,000 --> 01:03:46,750
Kwamba hukuweza kufanya\nmtihani wa ufadhili.

788
01:03:53,125 --> 01:03:53,958
Hata mimi.

789
01:03:57,208 --> 01:03:58,416
Kilichotokea siku hiyo...

790
01:03:59,500 --> 01:04:00,750
Sikukusudia. Kweli.

791
01:04:03,291 --> 01:04:05,041
Nisingejua kama\nulikusuadia au la.

792
01:04:05,750 --> 01:04:09,625
Ninachojua ni kwamba unahusika\nna kile kilichonitokea pia.

793
01:04:15,541 --> 01:04:17,333
Nina pendekezo kwako.

794
01:04:18,375 --> 01:04:19,208
Ni nini?

795
01:04:19,875 --> 01:04:20,833
Inahusu kufanya mtihani.

796
01:04:26,291 --> 01:04:27,958
Kufanya mtihani au kuiba kwenye mtihani?

797
01:04:28,666 --> 01:04:30,375
Kwangu mimi, kutumia neno "kuiba"

798
01:04:30,583 --> 01:04:32,416
inamaanisha kuna mtu anapoteza kitu.

799
01:04:34,625 --> 01:04:36,458
Lakini hapa, tutapata pesa\nna wengine watafaulu mitihani.

800
01:04:37,000 --> 01:04:37,875
Kila mtu anashinda.

801
01:04:45,250 --> 01:04:46,083
Bank.

802
01:04:47,916 --> 01:04:49,791
Sisi sote ni washindwa, kwa kweli.

803
01:04:51,041 --> 01:04:53,125
Hatukuzaliwa washindi\nkama Pat na Grace.

804
01:04:54,375 --> 01:04:57,583
Lazima tujitahidi zaidi ya wengine\nilikupata kile tunachostahili.

805
01:04:59,541 --> 01:05:00,583
Tazama kilichotokea.

806
01:05:00,666 --> 01:05:01,625
Sisi si sawa.

807
01:05:02,833 --> 01:05:03,750
Wewe uliiba.

808
01:05:05,208 --> 01:05:06,166
Lakini mimi sikuwa na bahati tu.

809
01:05:09,958 --> 01:05:10,791
Ni kweli.

810
01:05:12,208 --> 01:05:14,333
Lakini huoni\nkwamba hata usipoiba,

811
01:05:15,458 --> 01:05:17,041
maisha hukuhadaa vyovyote vile.

812
01:05:24,166 --> 01:05:25,291
Hii ni anwani ya nyumbani kwa Grace.

813
01:05:25,375 --> 01:05:26,750
Tuonane kesho ikiwa utapendezwa.

814
01:05:38,875 --> 01:05:42,416
WAPIGACHAPA WA BIASHARA YA UAMINIFU

815
01:05:42,500 --> 01:05:44,166
WAPIGACHAPA WA BIASHARA YA UAMINIFU

816
01:06:06,208 --> 01:06:07,833
FANYA KAZI KWA UFANISI

817
01:06:16,333 --> 01:06:17,291
Keti hapa.

818
01:06:19,291 --> 01:06:20,125
Habari.

819
01:06:20,833 --> 01:06:21,791
Hutaki kuketi?

820
01:06:33,416 --> 01:06:34,833
Hiki ndicho kitakachofanyika.

821
01:06:35,791 --> 01:06:40,625
Kwanza, mimi na wewe tutasafiri hadi Sydney, Australia\nna kufanya STIC pamoja.

822
01:06:51,125 --> 01:06:52,041
