823
01:06:53,875 --> 01:06:55,250
Unapungukiwa na hati moja.

824
01:06:56,583 --> 01:06:59,375
Baba, kile kipindi cha Teen Genius nilichoshiriki,

825
01:06:59,583 --> 01:07:01,166
