826
01:07:01,250 --> 01:07:03,125
KWA HISANI YA THAI LIFE INSURANCE

827
01:07:11,708 --> 01:07:14,000
Wanahitaji taarifa yako ya benki kwa ajili ya viza yangu.

828
01:07:14,416 --> 01:07:15,500
Unakwenda na nani?

829
01:07:16,125 --> 01:07:16,958
Ninakwenda na Bank.

830
01:07:20,083 --> 01:07:22,166
Siyo sisi tu.\nMwalimu wetu naye anakwenda.

831
01:07:26,250 --> 01:07:27,083
Pili,

832
01:07:27,416 --> 01:07:30,625
mimi na wewe kila mmoja atapaswa kukariri\nnusu ya maswali ya mtihani.

833
01:07:30,833 --> 01:07:31,833
Usisahau.

834
01:07:32,041 --> 01:07:34,333
Bank atakariri nusu ya kwanza,\nna Lynn nusu ya pili.

835
01:07:35,125 --> 01:07:36,708
Sehemu ya 1 ina maswali 52.

836
01:07:37,208 --> 01:07:38,041
