874
01:10:34,416 --> 01:10:36,041
Hiyo imezidi sana, Pat. Imezidi mno.

875
01:10:37,416 --> 01:10:39,250
Nimeshatumia kadi zangu zote.

876
01:10:39,375 --> 01:10:41,166
Mnafanya kana kwamba tumeshakamatwa kweli.

877
