Nimeshaelewa tayari.

878
01:10:43,583 --> 01:10:45,875
Mkikamatwa, tutakuacha ubebe lawama zote.

879
01:10:47,125 --> 01:10:49,875
Swali la mwisho kabla ya kuelekea uwanja wa ndege.

880
01:10:49,958 --> 01:10:50,833
Swali la mwisho.

881
01:10:56,083 --> 01:10:57,000
Tayari?

882
01:11:00,166 --> 01:11:01,625
Je, ikiwa Bank akikamatwa?

883
01:11:02,458 --> 01:11:03,625
Utasema nini?

884
01:11:07,916 --> 01:11:09,125
Hilo halinihusu hata kidogo.

885
01:11:09,583 --> 01:11:10,833
Sijawahi hata kuwa rafiki yake.

886
01:11:11,000 --> 01:11:13,000
Nimemwona shuleni kwa miaka minne au mitano iliyopita.

887
01:11:13,333 --> 01:11:14,875
Sijawahi kumwona akiwa na hata rafiki mmoja.

888
01:11:15,833 --> 01:11:17,125
Pia anaonekana kama mpuuzi.

889
01:11:17,375 --> 01:11:18,416
Na ni mtu wa ajabu.

890
01:11:19,458 --> 01:11:21,125
Hata alipigwa nje ya shule

