904
01:12:14,500 --> 01:12:16,000
Kuna nini? Nini? 

905
01:12:16,083 --> 01:12:17,625
-Mimi...
-Wewe... Nini sasa?

906
01:12:17,708 --> 01:12:18,916
Sijawahi kumwambia yeyote

907
01:12:19,333 --> 01:12:22,083
kwamba niliwahi kuamka kwenye rundo la takataka!

908
01:12:25,958 --> 01:12:27,916
Sasa, unajua kwa nini nimekasirika?

909
01:12:31,041 --> 01:12:32,583
Nyinyi nyote mlipanga hili, au siyo?

910
01:12:34,041 --> 01:12:36,333
Mlipanga ili nisiweze kufanya
